{"tid":1450114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「黑警還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:23:31.000Z","uid":202361,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e68852248959fb31e27c0623c2fe836af1077f5c","tid":1450114,"uid":202361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:20:11.000Z","msg":"唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2Smgqvltf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=adc54189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2Smgqvltf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=76feacc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"dc258ed3ba26758c0d192f43561d60a343191528","tid":1450114,"uid":102378,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:23:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各位手足 <br />\n聽日機場見<br />\n香港不應成為黑警天堂</span></span>"},{"pid":"db058d1f5c2082aefacb82ab296d70961e144eda","tid":1450114,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:23:31.000Z","msg":"［緊急］ 我呼籲 全民blackbloc！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1449581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1449581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nblack bloc原因唔係單純抗議，係要為升級鋪路！"}]}